import React from "react";
import { Navbar, Button, NavbarLink, NavbarContent, NavbarItem, NavbarBrand } from "@nextui-org/react";

const Header = () => {
  return (
      <Navbar isBordered variant="floating">
        <NavbarBrand>
        </NavbarBrand>
        <NavbarContent hideIn="xs">
          <NavbarLink href="#">Features</NavbarLink>
          <NavbarLink isActive href="#">Customers</NavbarLink>
          <NavbarLink href="#">Pricing</NavbarLink>
          <NavbarLink href="#">Company</NavbarLink>
        </NavbarContent>
        <Navbar.Content>
          <Navbar.Link color="inherit" href="#">
            Login
          </Navbar.Link>
          <Navbar.Item>
            <Button auto flat href="#">
              Sign Up
            </Button>
          </Navbar.Item>
        </Navbar.Content>
      </Navbar>
  )
}

export default Header;
